Protocol
------------------------------------------------------------------------

BeHappy Web communicates using the MVSy 1.0 protocol via a customized
GramJS-derived networking layer pointed at BeHappy backend servers.
MVSy 1.0 is independently developed and is not interoperable with
Telegram servers.

The MVSy 1.0 specification is available at:

    https://github.com/behappy-app/bh-mvsy

